Dear Users,
We are pleased to officially announce the introduction of a new library system, with effect from 14th May 2023. The implementation of the new system will improve Library system's functions, in addition to provide a greater user experience.
Therefore, please be informed that the following services has been made available immediately;
• Self-check (Borrowing)
• Book Return & Manual Book Drop (Returning)
• Renewal
• My Library Account
• Taylor's Catalogue
• Fines payment
We thank you for your kind patience, continuous support and cooperation.
Do not hesitate to contact us if you need further information on the new system via
Taylor's Library email at libraryenquiry@taylors.edu.my
